    "description": "Are you a skilled Surgeon looking for your next big career move? Neuland Laboratories in Pimpri-Chinchwad offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Neuland Laboratories:\nNeuland Laboratories is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Provide high-quality patient care and maintain patient records\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n• Administer medications and treatments as prescribed\n• Coordinate with multidisciplinary teams for comprehensive patient management\n• Monitor patient progress and adjust treatment plans accordingly\n• Maintain accurate clinical documentation in electronic health records\n• Respond to medical emergencies and provide immediate care\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Medical Coding\n• Proficiency in NABH Standards\n• Proficiency in Pharmacovigilance\n• Proficiency in HIPAA Compliance\n• Proficiency in Telemedicine\n• Proficiency in Wound Care\n• Proficiency in Patient Care\n• Proficiency in Diagnostic Skills\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pimpri-Chinchwad, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Neuland Laboratories!",
